00:01:04.580 --> 00:01:06.260
To place the loose glitter on the nail,

00:01:06.260 --> 00:01:07.960
we gotta make it sticky.

00:01:07.960 --> 00:01:10.260
So we do that by using a clear polish,

00:01:10.580 --> 00:01:11.680
NOT a top coat,

00:01:11.680 --> 00:01:13.780
because a top coat will get too thick,

00:01:13.780 --> 00:01:14.760
and dry too fast.

00:01:15.240 --> 00:01:16.540
And we just take some toothpicks,

00:01:16.740 --> 00:01:18.160
mine are cinnamon flavor,

00:01:18.160 --> 00:01:20.340
'cause I liked to lick things that are flavored.

00:01:20.340 --> 00:01:21.600
