00:01:21.600 --> 00:01:22.420
of the toothpick,

00:01:22.420 --> 00:01:25.100
and I really don't think I need to show you that on video.

00:01:25.100 --> 00:01:26.520
And then that's how you pick up

00:01:26.520 --> 00:01:27.680
the little piece of glitter.

00:01:28.340 --> 00:01:29.960
I like to start my glitter placements

00:01:29.960 --> 00:01:31.440
at the bottom of my nail,

00:01:31.440 --> 00:01:33.480
and then work my way to the top.

00:01:33.740 --> 00:01:34.240
But,

00:01:34.240 --> 00:01:35.040
I'm no expert.

00:01:35.040 --> 00:01:36.920
Honestly, this is only like the second time

00:01:36.920 --> 00:01:38.760
