00:02:51.880 --> 00:02:54.060
grade seven at sleepover camp.

00:02:54.060 --> 00:02:55.540
Those were the 'Good ol' days!'

00:02:55.540 --> 00:02:58.080
But now we do it with glitter on our nails!

00:02:58.080 --> 00:02:59.160
It's just so much more fun!

00:02:59.160 --> 00:03:01.400
Why didn't I do this when I was in grade 7?

00:03:01.400 --> 00:03:01.900
Why?

