The sides are always a little tricky,

00:03:04.040 --> 00:03:05.960
because if you're like me and human,

00:03:05.960 --> 00:03:08.460
our cuticles are not hexagon shaped.

00:03:08.460 --> 00:03:09.660
So you're gonna hafta like,

00:03:09.660 --> 00:03:11.660
move them around and make it work.

00:03:11.660 --> 00:03:12.160
Alright!

00:03:12.160 --> 00:03:13.520
